                    <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm mb-3">Search the web for sites that explain these 5 topics:</p>
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-2 text-[11px] font-bold">
                        <span class="bg-slate-100 p-2 rounded">A) THE PASSIVE VOICE IN ENGLISH</span>
                        <span class="bg-slate-100 p-2 rounded">B) TWO OBJECTS AS SUBJECT</span>
                        <span class="bg-slate-100 p-2 rounded">C) WHEN TO OMIT THE AGENT</span>
                        <span class="bg-slate-100 p-2 rounded">D) PASSIVE WITH REPORTING VERBS</span>
                        <span class="bg-slate-100 p-2 rounded">E) THE CAUSATIVE (HAVE/GET DONE)</span>
                    </div>
