        <!-- Phase 2 -->
        <section class="mb-12">
            <h3 class="text-indigo-600 font-black uppercase text-xs tracking-widest mb-4">Phase 2: Training NotebookLM</h3>
            <div class="success-step p-6 shadow-md">
                <h4 class="font-bold text-green-800 text-xl mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
                    <i class="fas fa-paper-plane"></i> 4. Important Step: Send the Chat Instruction
                </h4>
                <p class="text-slate-700 text-sm mb-4">In the CHAT on NotebookLM, paste the text below. <strong>YOU MUST SEND THE MESSAGE AND WAIT FOR THE RESPONSE</strong> before moving to Gemini.</p>
                
                <div class="copy-box p-4 relative mb-4">
                    <pre id="masterPrompt" class="text-[11px] text-slate-800 whitespace-pre-wrap leading-tight">Create a comprehensive educative interactive lesson for the passive voice. Explain every aspect:
A) THE PASSIVE VOICE IN ENGLISH
B) THE USE OF TWO OBJECTS AS SUBJECT OF THE PASSIVE
C) WHEN TO OMIT THE AGENT
D) THE PASSIVE VOICE WITH REPORTING VERBS (eg. He is said to ...)
E) THE USE OF THE CAUSATIVE (HAVE/GET SOMETHING DONE)

With every explanation there must be sentences in English as example and their translation into Spanish.

All the sentences in English must have their native audio.
There must be an EXERCISES SECTION with as many modules as the topics seen in the explanation. Each module of exercises must have 10 different sentences/exercises to do. Exercises must be fill-in the gaps. Only one answer is possible. If there are more than one possible answer, admit both. Exercises don’t have into account capital letters nor punctuation marks. Exercises are self-assessed with explanations when the student fails.

This app must start with a field the student has to fill in with their name and surname.
At the end of each module of exercises, there must be a partial score. When the student finishes all the modules, there must be a final score with the student’s name.
The user interface must be professional, clean, and clear.</pre>
                    <button onclick="copyText('masterPrompt')" class="absolute top-2 right-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-lg text-xs hover:bg-indigo-800 font-bold transition-all shadow-lg">COPY ALL TEXT</button>
                </div>
                <p class="text-xs font-black text-green-700 uppercase italic">Be sure you have selected all the sources before sending this chat!</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Phase 3 -->
        <section class="mb-12">
