            <div class="step-card bg-white p-6 rounded-r-xl shadow-sm mb-6">
                <h4 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">5. Create a NEW GEM</h4>
                <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm mb-4">Open <a href="https://gemini.google.com/" target="_blank" class="text-indigo-600 underline font-bold">Gemini</a>. Click the 3 lines (Top Left) &gt; <strong>ADD A NEW GEM</strong>.</p>
                <ol class="list-decimal ml-6 text-sm text-slate-700 space-y-2">
                    <li>Name it (e.g., <strong>PASSIVE VOICE</strong>).</li>
                    <li>Instructions: PASTE the same text you wrote in your NotebookLM chat.</li>
                    <li>Start the CHAT.</li>
                </ol>
            </div>

            <div class="alert-manual p-6 mb-6">
                <h4 class="text-red-700 font-black mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
                    <i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle"></i> IF YOU CAN'T CONNECT NOTEBOOKLM (Troubleshooting)
                </h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-slate-800 mb-4 font-medium">If Gemini doesn't show your sources automatically, use this manual method:</p>
                <div class="bg-white/50 p-4 rounded-lg text-sm space-y-3 border border-red-200">
                    <p><strong>1. Copy the Content:</strong> Copy the answer that NotebookLM gave you and the text from your research websites.</p>
                    <p><strong>2. Create a Document:</strong> Paste everything into a Word or Google Doc and save it.</p>
                    <p><strong>3. Upload to Gemini:</strong> In the Gemini chat, click <strong>"+" (Plus)</strong> &gt; <strong>"Upload from this device"</strong> and select your saved document.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="step-card bg-white p-6 rounded-r-xl shadow-sm">
                <h4 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">6. Generate and Preview</h4>
                <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">In Gemini: Select <strong>CANVAS</strong>. Paste the Master Prompt again and send. Wait for the code, then click <strong>"VISTA PREVIA"</strong>.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Phase 4 -->
        <section class="mb-12 bg-slate-200/50 p-8 rounded-3xl">
